{"channel":"首页>组织机构>事业单位>安全技术中心>安全大视角","content":"<div class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\"> \n <p>　　2011年3月11日东日本大地震后，日本新干线地震监测预警系统（早期地震检测系统）不断改进，增设地震监测预警系统监测点，改进系统性能，在地震波到达铁路线之前尽量使列车减速或停车。</p> \n <p>　　近日，新干线脱轨对策协议会事务局发布了直至2014年度末新干线地震监测预警系统强化措施的推进情况。</p> \n <p align=\"center\">东日本地震后新干线地震监测预警系统的改进</p> \n <div align=\"center\"> \n  <table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; width: 426.1pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-yfti-tbllook: 480; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; mso-border-insideh: .5pt solid windowtext; mso-border-insidev: .5pt solid windowtext\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"568\" border=\"1\"> \n   <tbody> \n    <tr style=\"height: 24.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes\"> \n     <td style=\"border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 24.25pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; width: 63pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"84\" nowrap> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">公司名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></font></b></p> </td> \n     <td style=\"border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 24.25pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-right: 5.4pt; width: 135pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\